[[[description]]]
Fetches the constant flags of a [`zval`](https://phpinternals.net/docs/zval). These flags are used for specifying the constant type (whether it is a class constant, namespaced, qualified, etc), as well as the [class fetching type](https://phpinternals.net/categories/zend_classes#class-fetching).

This macro also has a counterpart macro, `Z_CONST_FLAGS_P`, that accepts a pointer to a [`zval`](https://phpinternals.net/docs/zval) instead.

